News Releases, Media Advisories

October 10, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
DIANE E. WATSON FOR CONGRESS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on Diane E. Watson for Congress (CA 33rd District). This audit covers the period of February 7, 2001 through December 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: Final Audit Report on Diane E. Watson for Congress Made Available
